❗️Results of the meeting of the Committee on Human Rights On April 9, a meeting of the Committee was held, based on the results of which it was recommended:

- the project of the Law of Ukraine on amendments to Article 11 of the Law of Ukraine "On the Legal Status of Persons Disappeared Under Special Circumstances" (No. 11093) as a result of the consideration in the first reading to return to the subject the right of legislative initiative for revision;

- the draft Law of Ukraine on appeals (No. 11082) based on the results of consideration in the first reading to be accepted as a basis;

- the draft Law of Ukraine on amendments to the Civil Procedure Code of Ukraine, the Economic Procedure Code of Ukraine, the Code of Administrative Procedure of Ukraine regarding access to justice for persons with disabilities (No. 11132) as a basis for consideration in the first reading.

The members of the Committee also considered the annual report of the Commissioner for Human Rights of the Verkhovna Rada of Ukraine on the state of observance and protection of human and citizen rights and freedoms in Ukraine in 2023. 📲Details
